                    <p class="bold">
                      By enrolling for PharmaNet access, you agree to the following terms (the “Agreement”). Please read them carefully.
                    </p>

                    <ol>
                      <li>

                        <p class="bold underline">
                          On Behalf of User Access
                        </p>

                        <p class="bold">
                          You represent and warrant to the Province that:
                        </p>

                        <ol type="a">
                          <li>
