                          </li>
                          <li>

                            <p>
                              <strong>Non Compliance.</strong> You will promptly notify the Province, and provide particulars, if:
                            </p>

                            <ol type="i">
                              <li>
                                you or an On-Behalf-of User do not comply, or you anticipate that you or a On-Behalf-of User will be unable
